<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Alertă Stoc Piese</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        h1 { color: #d35400; border-bottom: 2px solid #d35400; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: white; margin-top: 20px; }
        th, td { padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        th { background-color: #e67e22; color: white; }
        tr:nth-child(even) { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
        .back-btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; background: #34495e; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        .status-low { color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Vizualizare Simplă (Stoc Critic Piese)</h1>
    <p>Această pagină afișează datele din <strong>V_PIESE_STOC</strong> (Piese cu stoc < 20).</p>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>ID PIESĂ</th>
                <th>DENUMIRE PIESĂ</th>
                <th>STOC DISPONIBIL</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% date.forEach(piesa => { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= piesa.ID_PIESA %></td>
                    <td><%= piesa.DENUMIRE_PIESA %></td>
                    <td class="status-low"><%= piesa.STOC_DISPONIBIL %> buc.</td>
                </tr>
            <% }) %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Înapoi la Panoul Principal</a>
</body>
</html>